for using with pytest command in terminal

--headed - for showing browser window during execution
--slowmo=500 - slowing down the browser
--browser=firefox - changing the browser
--device='Pixel 5' - emulate a testing device
--tracing (on / off / retain-on-failure) - will provide or not provide test results in zip file in test-result directory
--video on - will create a video for each test
--screenshot on - will create a screenshot after the test is done
--screenshot only-on-failure - will create a screenshot only the test failed
-k {test name} - will only collect the test name to run


